ğŸš© Troubleshooting
Streamlit not found:
Make sure Streamlit is installed:
    pip install streamlit

CSV encoding issues:
  Ensure you export using UTF-8 encoding.

Modify the CSV export line if needed:
  csv = df.to_csv(index=False, encoding='utf-8').encode('utf-8')

